            <p>The tallest bar marks the month with the strongest overall activation â€” not necessarily â€œgoodâ€ or â€œbad,â€ but a time when feelings, clarity, and self-awareness may be especially heightened.</p>

            <h3><span role="img" aria-label="Target">ðŸŽ¯</span> Why this is different</h3>
            <p>Most forecasts generalize for everyone. This chart is calculated for <em>your</em> birth Sun position, your unique sensitivity profile, and your dominant monthly aspect â€” making it a personalized map of emotional rhythms rather than a one-size-fits-all horoscope.</p>

